# Ledger Snippets

### Policy edits ledger entry

**When roles are edited,** emit a single, normalized ledger event:

domain="governance", 
type="policy_change", 
operation="set",
target_id=None (or a synthetic governance ULID if you prefer),
changed_fields_json={"entity.allowed_roles": {"from": [...], "to": [...]}}.

That gives you a clean, consistent trail.
